      'summary': 'Tests run successfully. The project is a minimal Python 3.12 project using uv + pytest. Two tests pass, one (`test_impossible`) always fails by design. The key fix needed was setting `PYTHONPATH=/project_src` in `run_all_tests.sh` so pytest could import the `app` module since the project source is not installed as a package. The `uv sync --locked` in the Dockerfile pre-warms all dependencies for fast layer caching.',
